      ]},
      {"id": "col_story_r", "elType": "column", "settings": {"_column_size": 60, "content_position": "top"}, "elements": [
        {"id": "w_story_p1", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": {"editor": "<p>For over three decades, Billy Beck III has been at the forefront of elite personal training — transforming the bodies and minds of champions, Hollywood talent, Fortune 500 executives, and clients who simply refuse to settle. His methodology is uncompromising, his approach data-driven, his results — documented.</p>", "text_color": "#cfcfcf", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Inter", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 17}, "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.75}, "_margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "20", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}},
        {"id": "w_story_p2", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": {"editor": "<p>Twice crowned <strong>World's Best Personal Trainer</strong> by MET-Rx — a distinction won against the top trainers on the planet. Inducted into the <strong>Fitness Hall of Fame</strong>. Named <strong>Trainer of the Year</strong> by industry peers. Featured in Muscle &amp; Fitness, Men's Health, GQ, Rolling Stone, and on ABC, NBC, CBS, and FOX.</p>", "text_color": "#cfcfcf", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Inter", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 17}, "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.75}, "_margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "20", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}},
        {"id": "w_story_p3", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": {"editor": "<p>But the real story isn't the accolades — it's the thousand-plus transformations. Real people. Real receipts. No filters, no shortcuts, no BS.</p>", "text_color": "#9a9a9a", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Inter", "typography_font_style": "italic", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 18}, "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.65}}}
      ]}
    ]
  },
